description: Update one or more parameters for the sequence store.

parameters.name: id
parameters.description: The ID of the sequence store.

parameters.name: clientToken
parameters.description: To ensure that requests don't run multiple times, specify a unique token for each request. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

parameters.name: propagatedSetLevelTags
parameters.description: The tags keys to propagate to the S3 objects associated with read sets in the sequence store. (string) ---

parameters.name: s3AccessConfig
parameters.description: S3 access configuration parameters. accessLogLocation (string) --- Location of the access logs.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The ID of the sequence store.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the sequence store.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the sequence store.

nested_items.name: sseConfig
nested_items.description: Server-side encryption (SSE) settings for a store.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The time when the store was created.

nested_items.name: updateTime
nested_items.description: The last-updated time of the Sequence Store.

nested_items.name: propagatedSetLevelTags
nested_items.description: The tags keys to propagate to the S3 objects associated with read sets in the sequence store.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the sequence store.

nested_items.name: statusMessage
nested_items.description: The status message of the sequence store.

nested_items.name: fallbackLocation
nested_items.description: The S3 URI of a bucket and folder to store Read Sets that fail to upload.

nested_items.name: s3Uri
nested_items.description: The S3 URI of the sequence store.

nested_items.name: s3AccessPointArn
nested_items.description: This is ARN of the access point associated with the S3 bucket storing read sets.

nested_items.name: eTagAlgorithmFamily
nested_items.description: The ETag algorithm family to use on ingested read sets.
